properties.Name: Protocol
properties.Description:
A protocol that may be associated with a component.

Ex:
- 1-Wire
- ANSI C12.18
- BACnet
- BSAP
- CANopen
- C-Bus
- CC-Link I 
- CC-Link Industrial Networks
- CIP (Common Industrial Protocol)
- Controller Area Network
- ControlNet
- DALI
- DeviceNet
- DF-1
- DirectNet
- DLMS/IEC 62056
- DNP3
- DSI
- EtherCAT
- Ethernet Global Data (EGD)
- EtherNet/IP Ethernet Powerlink
- Foundation Fieldbus H1
- FOUNDATION fieldbus HSE (High Speed Ethernet)
- GE SRTP
- Honeywell SDS
- HostLink Protocol
- IEC 60870-5
- IEC 61107
- IEC 61850
- IEC 62351
- Interbus
- Konnex (KNX)
- LonTalk
- M-Bus
- Modbus PEMEX
- Modbus Plus
- Modbus RTU
- oBIX
- Optomux
- Profibus
- RAPIEnet
- P-Net
- S-Bus
- SERCOS III
- Sinec H1
- SwiftNet (a protocol developed for Boeing, since withdrawn)
- SynqNet
- MTConnect
- OPC
- OPC UA
- WorldFIP
- xAP
- ZigBee
- ZigBee Smart Energy 2.0
